text: Kenia Kristel Rangel Villareal (born 6 August 1995) is a Panamanian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Israeli Ligat Nashim club Maccabi Holon FC and the Panama women's national team. ==International career== Rangel appeared in five matches for Panama and scored one goal at the 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship. She scored a hat trick against El Salvador in a 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship qualification match. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Maccabi Holon F.C.
